 string ^           (size is  1000)   0.284    0.035                0.062    0.050
 concat string list (size is     3)   0.020    0.020
 concat string list (size is  1000)   1.752    0.116                0.240    0.115
 concat string list (size is 10000)  16.957    0.632                2.087    0.462
